1. *Naučili* smo mnogo o istoriji našeg grada. (We learned a lot about the history of our city.)
2. Oni su *naučili* strani jezik za samo nekoliko meseci. (They learned a foreign language in just a few months.)
3. Kada su me *naučili* da vozim, osećao sam se kao da sam dobio krila. (When they taught me how to drive, I felt like I had wings.)
4. Njihova majka ih je *naučila* kako da budu strpljivi i istrajni. (Their mother taught them how to be patient and persistent.)
5. Oni su *naučeni* da poštuju autoritete. (They were taught to respect authority.)
6. Ja bih voleo da sam *naučio* da sviram gitaru kada sam bio mlađi. (I wish I had learned to play the guitar when I was younger.)
7. *Naučite* me kako da napravim ovaj kolač. (Teach me how to make this cake.)
8. *Naučiću* taj trik ako mi pokažeš kako se radi. (I will learn that trick if you show me how to do it.)
9. *Naučio* sam lekciju o tome da nikada ne treba verovati lažovima. (I learned a lesson about never trusting liars.)
10. Kada su *naučeni* da rade zajedno, ova grupa ljudi postala je veoma efikasna. (When they were taught to work together, this group of people became very efficient.)